{
  "stem": "1799.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first thing that happened, really, was Sukkot, Sukkot of 1938-- the Succah was still up-- is when my father-- there, there were the-- police came to the house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in early October of 1938.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Police came to the house with a warrant, address warrant-- arrest warrant-- and my father was being taken to the local police station.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it turned out, subsequently, we learned that somebody had called in to say that he killed chickens the kosher way, which was against the law, which he did.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he, you know, it was, it was something that everybody knew, but he was turned into the authorities.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we expected him to just be given a slap on the hand and be excused.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, instead he was convicted to six months in prison, which was a shock, especially to my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, she had the table set for the day he was in court with his attorney, to have a party at 4 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have it set with our finest china, and all, to celebrate his return.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had been gone about a week in the police station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, he didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was sent to jail, and that was a shock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was soon after that-- when she realized my father was in prison for six months, couldn't do much about it-- that she then sent me to a home in Berlin, first to my family in Berlin, and then to a home.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was actually an orphanage, because she felt that her activities were such that she would do better in not encumbering herself with her children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in trying to help my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
